771
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:14,760
Hindi.

772
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:17,320
Huwag pumutok ito ng walang sukat.
mahal kita.

773
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:22,960
ayos lang.

774
